name: Through the Eyes of a Stranger

metadata.name: Blazing eyes.
metadata.description: Try to appreciate the phrase "Knows how to keep a face. Many people hold themselves well in society, have a confident gait, a good stance. But almost everyone has examples where all the confidence melts away. She never made eye contact, maybe that's what beckoned passersby so much. There was a lot of talk about her, which already set her apart from the general mass. As much as she wanted to, happiness didn't come with the beauty she was given. Blinded by beauty, men's gazes followed her until they lost sight of her. Women's, on the other hand, as if they did not notice at all. What a pity the sixteenth century was so cruel. Under the flame of fire, not a muscle trembled on her flawless face. Under the flame of fire, everyone gathered felt her bottomless, mesmerizing gaze, as if peering into her soul in the last moments of her life.
